            </div>
            
            <div class="price-breakdown">
                <div class="breakdown-item">
                    <span class="breakdown-label">üè∑Ô∏è Original Price:</span>
                    <span class="breakdown-value original" id="popup-original-price">$0.00</span>
                </div>
                <div class="breakdown-item">
                    <span class="breakdown-label">üî• Sale Price:</span>
                    <span class="breakdown-value sale" id="popup-sale-price">$0.00</span>
                </div>
                <div class="breakdown-item discount-applied">
                    <span class="breakdown-label">‚ö° Special Discount Applied:</span>
                    <span class="breakdown-value discount" id="popup-discount-amount">-$0.00</span>
                </div>
                <div class="breakdown-divider"></div>
                <div class="breakdown-item final-price">
                    <span class="breakdown-label">üéØ Your Final Price:</span>
                    <span class="breakdown-value final" id="popup-final-price">$0.00</span>
                </div>
                <div class="breakdown-item total-savings">
                    <span class="breakdown-label">üíµ Total Savings:</span>
                    <span class="breakdown-value savings" id="popup-total-savings">$0.00</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="discount-features">
                <h4>üåü What Makes This Deal Special:</h4>
                <ul class="features-list">
                    <li>‚úÖ Exclusive limited-time discount</li>
                    <li>‚úÖ No minimum order requirements</li>
                    <li>‚úÖ Stackable with other promotions</li>
